title: 3 bedrooms near NEU
posting_body: ['Top floor 3 bedrooms, no livingroom.', 'Unit Features:', 'Built-in Closet Ceramic Tiles Dining Room Dishwasher Disposal Duplex Eat-in Kitchen Exposed Brick Granite Counter Tops Hardwood Floors High Ceiling Lighting Loft Microwave Modern Bath Modern Kitchen Roof-Top Access Stainless Steel Appliance(s)', 'Building Features:', '2 Passenger Elevators Concierge Concierge Services Elevator Enclosed Landscaped Courtyard Fitness Center indoor pool open year round Laundry in Building LOUNGE W/ POOL TABLE & SMART TV State-of-the-art Fitness Center STUDY W/ APPLE COMPUTERS, common yard', 'This former factory historic building is located in the heart of the South End, within walking distance to hospitals, universities, public transportation and city life entertainment.', "Don't feel like leaving the comfort of the indoors?", 'Enjoy some time in our indoor heated pool or take a stroll in the Art Gallery located right in your building.', 'This building has 177 individually designed lofts with an array of floor plan where no units are exactly the same.']
